    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $5,500 and is offered in poor condition \u2014 we believe in full transparency so buyers can make informed decisions. The exterior shows considerable wear, including visible scratches, dents, and paint fading in multiple areas. The interior has seen heavy use, with worn upholstery, staining, and some trim pieces that are cracked or missing. Mechanically, the vehicle runs but has known issues that will likely require attention, making it best suited for a buyer comfortable with repairs or someone looking for a project car or parts vehicle. This is a budget option priced accordingly, and we encourage any serious buyer to arrange a pre-purchase inspection so there are absolutely no surprises.",
