    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Great Condition, Great Value \u2014 A Dependable Good Condition Gem!\n\nReady for a vehicle that truly delivers? This car is in genuinely good condition \u2014 well-maintained, mechanically sound, and a pleasure to drive! The exterior shows only minor signs of normal use, and the interior is clean and comfortable. It starts right up, handles confidently, and gives you that reliable feeling every time you hit the road. No major issues to worry about \u2014 just a solid, trustworthy vehicle ready for its next owner. If you're looking for quality without the mint-condition price tag, this is a smart, honest choice you'll feel good about!",
      "price": 33500.0,
