    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Meet your next chapter. This stunning machine arrives wearing its years with quiet confidence \u2014 the kind of car that turns heads not by trying, but simply by being. Slide into the driver's seat and feel the world rearrange itself around you. Every surface tells a story of careful ownership, every mile a memory preserved with pride. The engine hums with the easy authority of something that has been loved, not just driven. Whether you're chasing weekend horizons or commanding the daily commute, this is the car that makes every journey feel like the one worth remembering. Opportunities like this don't wait \u2014 and neither should you.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
