      "description": "This exceptional vehicle is the definition of mint condition \u2014 meticulously maintained, spotlessly clean inside and out, and performing exactly as it should. Every surface, system, and component reflects the care of a conscientious owner. Whether you're behind the wheel or glancing back at it in the parking lot, this car turns heads for all the right reasons. Low miles, flawless finish, and a service history that speaks for itself. Don't miss your chance to own a vehicle that truly stands apart from the crowd.",
